\c 7  
\s1 The right attitude toward others  
\m
\v 1 “\w Do|strong="G2919"\w* \w not|strong="G3361"\w* \w judge|strong="G2919"\w*, \w so|strong="G2443"\w* \w that|strong="G2443"\w* \w you|strong="G3361"\w* \w be|strong="G3361"\w* \w not|strong="G3361"\w* \w judged|strong="G2919"\w*.\f + \fr 7:1 \ft By whom? Perhaps both God and man.\f*  
