\v 3 \w So|strong="G1161"\w* \w why|strong="G5101"\w* \w do|strong="G5101"\w* \w you|strong="G4771"\w* \w look|strong="G2657"\w* \w at|strong="G1722"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w speck|strong="G2595"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w your|strong="G4674"\w* brother's \w eye|strong="G3788"\w* \w but|strong="G1161"\w* \w do|strong="G5101"\w* \w not|strong="G3756"\w* \w consider|strong="G2657"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* plank \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w your|strong="G4674"\w* \w own|strong="G4674"\w* \w eye|strong="G3788"\w*?  
