\s2 A tree is known by its fruit  
\p
\v 15 “\w Beware|strong="G4337"\w* \w of|strong="G1722"\w* \w false|strong="G5578"\w* \w prophets|strong="G5578"\w* \w who|strong="G3588"\w* \w come|strong="G2064"\w* \w to|strong="G4314"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w sheep|strong="G4263"\w*'s \w clothing|strong="G1742"\w*, \w but|strong="G1161"\w* \w inwardly|strong="G2081"\w* \w they|strong="G1161"\w* \w are|strong="G1510"\w* ravenous \w wolves|strong="G3074"\w*.\f + \fr 7:15 \ft Probably demonized; demonic prophecies are always destructive.\f*  
\v 16 \w You|strong="G1438"\w* \w will|strong="G3385"\w* \w know|strong="G1921"\w* \w them|strong="G3588"\w* \w by|strong="G2228"\w* \w their|strong="G1438"\w* \w fruits|strong="G2590"\w*. \w Do|strong="G2228"\w* \w people|strong="G3588"\w* \w gather|strong="G4816"\w* \w grapes|strong="G4718"\w* \w from|strong="G3588"\w* thorn bushes, \w or|strong="G2228"\w* \w figs|strong="G4810"\w* \w from|strong="G3588"\w* \w thistles|strong="G5146"\w*?  
