\s1 Jesus heals at a distance\f + \fr 8:5 \ft It has often been assumed that this account is parallel to that in Luke 7:1-10, but I believe they were different occasions. For a detailed discussion, please see the Appendix: Did the centurion leave his house?\f*  
\p
