\s1 Jesus controls wind and wave  
\p
\v 23 \w Now|strong="G2532"\w* \w when|strong="G2532"\w* \w He|strong="G2532"\w* \w got|strong="G1684"\w* \w into|strong="G1519"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w boat|strong="G4143"\w*, \w His|strong="G1519"\w* \w disciples|strong="G3101"\w* followed \w Him|strong="G3588"\w*.  
