\s1 A tough kind of demon  
\p
\v 14 \w As|strong="G2532"\w* \w they|strong="G2532"\w* \w came|strong="G2064"\w* \w to|strong="G4314"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w crowd|strong="G3793"\w* \w a|strong="G2532"\w* man \w approached|strong="G4334"\w* \w Him|strong="G3588"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w kneeling|strong="G2532"\w* \w to|strong="G4314"\w* \w Him|strong="G3588"\w* \w said|strong="G2532"\w*:  
