\s1 Handling a recalcitrant brother  
\p
\v 15 “\w Now|strong="G1161"\w* \w if|strong="G1437"\w* \w your|strong="G1437"\w* brother sins \w against|strong="G1519"\w* \w you|strong="G4771"\w*, \w go|strong="G5217"\w*, confront \w him|strong="G3588"\w* \w between|strong="G3342"\w* \w you|strong="G4771"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w him|strong="G3588"\w* \w alone|strong="G3441"\w*. \w If|strong="G1437"\w* \w he|strong="G2532"\w* hears \w you|strong="G4771"\w*, \w you|strong="G4771"\w* \w have|strong="G2532"\w* \w won|strong="G2770"\w* \w your|strong="G1437"\w* brother.  
