\v 19 Stupid \w and|strong="G3173"\w* \w blind|strong="G5185"\w*!! \w For|strong="G1063"\w* \w which|strong="G3588"\w* \w is|strong="G3588"\w* \w greater|strong="G3173"\w*, \w the|strong="G3588"\w* \w gift|strong="G1435"\w* \w or|strong="G2228"\w* \w the|strong="G3588"\w* \w altar|strong="G2379"\w* \w that|strong="G3588"\w* sanctifies \w the|strong="G3588"\w* \w gift|strong="G1435"\w*?\f + \fr 23:19 \ft Wow, they really were stupid and blind! which raises the obvious question: How did they get that way? According to Ephesians 2:2, ‘sons of the disobedience’ suffer direct satanic influence.\f*  
\v 20 \w Therefore|strong="G3767"\w* \w he|strong="G2532"\w* \w who|strong="G3588"\w* \w swears|strong="G3660"\w* \w by|strong="G1722"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w altar|strong="G2379"\w* \w swears|strong="G3660"\w* \w by|strong="G1722"\w* \w it|strong="G2532"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w by|strong="G1722"\w* \w all|strong="G3956"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w things|strong="G3956"\w* \w on|strong="G1722"\w* \w it|strong="G2532"\w*.  
