\s1 The increase of lawlessness  
\p
\v 9 “\w Then|strong="G2532"\w* \w they|strong="G2532"\w* \w will|strong="G1510"\w* \w hand|strong="G3860"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w over|strong="G3860"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* oppression \w and|strong="G2532"\w* kill \w you|strong="G5210"\w*, \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w will|strong="G1510"\w* \w be|strong="G1510"\w* \w hated|strong="G3404"\w* \w by|strong="G1223"\w* \w all|strong="G3956"\w* \w nations|strong="G1484"\w* \w for|strong="G1519"\w* \w my|strong="G3956"\w* \w name|strong="G3686"\w*'s \w sake|strong="G1223"\w*.  
